import React from 'react'
import {
  Routes,
  Route
} from 'react-router-dom'
import { TransitionGroup, CSSTransition } from 'react-transition-group'

import ScrollToTop from './ScrollToTop'
import Home from '../Pages/Home'
import About from '../Pages/About'
import Experience from '../Pages/Experience'
import CallCenterDashboard from '../Pages/Case-Studies/CallCenterDashboard'
import BUCallsLeadsFeature from '../Pages/Case-Studies/BUCallsLeadsFeature'
import CampaignInterface from '../Pages/Case-Studies/CampaignInterface'
import AdvertiserOnboarding from '../Pages/Case-Studies/AdvertiserOnboarding'
import AdditionalProjects from '../Pages/Case-Studies/AdditionalProjects'
import CreativeProjects from '../Pages/Case-Studies/CreativeProjects'
import LovingWithFood from '../Pages/Case-Studies/LovingWithFood'


class Main extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return(
      <main>
        <ScrollToTop>
          <Routes location={location}>
            <Route path='/' element={<About />}/>
            <Route path='/experience' component={Experience}/>
            <Route path='/case-studies' component={Home}/>
            <Route path='/case-studies/call-center-dashboard' component={CallCenterDashboard}/>
            <Route path='/case-studies/calls-leads-feature' component={BUCallsLeadsFeature}/>
            <Route path='/case-studies/additional-projects' component={AdditionalProjects}/>
            <Route path='/case-studies/advertiser-onboarding' component={AdvertiserOnboarding}/>
            <Route path='/case-studies/campaign-interface' component={CampaignInterface}/>
            <Route path='/case-studies/creative-direction' component={CreativeProjects}/>
            <Route path='/case-studies/loving-with-food' component={LovingWithFood}/>
          </Routes>
          {/*<Routes render={({ location }) => (
            <TransitionGroup>
              <CSSTransition
                key={location.key}
                timeout={300}
                classNames='fade'
              >
              </CSSTransition>
            </TransitionGroup>
          )}/>*/}
        </ScrollToTop>
      </main>
    )
  }
}

export default Main
